abstract: Revenue at the network equipment maker rose 8 percent in the second quarter. The financial performance exceeded expectations.

lead_paragraph: John T. Chambers, the chief executive of Cisco Systems, prides himself on forecasting technology and economic shifts ahead of his company’s peers and competitors.

headline.print_headline: Cisco Profit Rises 23% on Better-Than-Expected Sales
